the Love Mansion for the first time)

331
00:17:39,552 --> 00:17:41,004
- Hello.
- Hello.

332
00:17:41,331 --> 00:17:43,831
- What's going on?
- I'm so curious!

333
00:17:47,298 --> 00:17:49,878
- So that's what the couples are based on?
- No way.

334
00:17:49,903 --> 00:17:50,903
For real?

335
00:17:51,063 --> 00:17:53,682
- When was this?
- Yesterday.

336
00:17:53,836 --> 00:17:56,703
- The one across from us?
- Is that right?

337
00:17:57,228 --> 00:18:00,006
No way. Their partner is the
one sitting across from them?

338
00:18:00,709 --> 00:18:02,391
- Seriously?
- Are you serious?

339
00:18:02,587 --> 00:18:04,792
(Your partner is the one
who sat across from you when

340
00:18:04,817 --> 00:18:06,816
the 10 of you met for
the first time last night.)

341
00:18:07,803 --> 00:18:09,564
- Wow.
- Who sat across from me?

342
00:18:09,934 --> 00:18:11,600
Wow, so this is how it's happening.

343
00:18:11,625 --> 00:18:14,649
(Today's Couples)

344
00:18:14,867 --> 00:18:16,803
(Random matching)

345
00:18:16,828 --> 00:18:19,838
This is really random!
You can't blame anyone for this.

346
00:18:20,627 --> 00:18:22,674
What do I do?
It's going to be so interesting!

347
00:18:22,699 --> 00:18:25,099
Ji-min is partners with Ha-neul.

348
00:18:25,124 --> 00:18:26,991
- Oh, you're right.
- Yeah.

349
00:18:27,016 --> 00:18:29,437
- Da-Na is with Jung-woo?
- Yes!

350
00:18:29,462 --> 00:18:31,111
- Oh, yeah, she is!
- You're right.

351
00:18:31,136 --> 00:18:32,621
I'm really curious about them.

352
00:18:33,802 --> 00:18:35,870
(She predicts there will
be big entertainment.)

353
00:18:38,766 --> 00:18:43,402
But there are some couples
we've never seen together before.

354
00:18:43,608 --> 00:18:45,745
- I'm really curious about
the concept. - Me, too.

355
00:18:45,770 --> 00:18:49,781
(The five men are waiting for
their partners for today's challenge.)

356
00:18:49,806 --> 00:18:54,094
Su-won will be conscious
of Ha-neul a lot today, too.

357
00:18:54,877 --> 00:18:58,379
- Oh, hey.
- Hi, Su-won.

358
00:18:58,938 --> 00:19:00,471
- Let's go.
- Alright.

359
00:19:02,151 --> 00:19:03,651
Did you prepare well?

360
00:19:03,676 --> 00:19:06,734
- We're not doing something fierce, are we?
- Dunno. I feel like we are.

361
00:19:06,759 --> 00:19:09,735
- Right?
- I look like that, too.

362
00:19:09,760 --> 00:19:12,231
- Do I look fierce?
- Honestly speaking, yes.

363
00:19:12,256 --> 00:19:13,256
Really?

364
00:19:13,489 --> 00:19:14,965
Isn't that a bad thing?

365
00:19:14,990 --> 00:19:18,610
No, what I mean is that
you're lively and nice.

366
00:19:18,772 --> 00:19:20,430
You're talking quickly now.

367
00:19:22,427 --> 00:19:23,427
It's Jung-woo.

368
00:19:23,452 --> 00:19:26,014
(Jung-woo & Da-Na couple)

369
00:19:26,039 --> 00:19:27,835
- She's thrilled.
- Hey.

370
00:19:27,860 --> 00:19:28,860
Oh, hi.

371
00:19:31,811 --> 00:19:33,302
- This way?
- Yes.

372
00:19:34,433 --> 00:19:37,053
- You're dazzling.
- Thank you.

373
00:19:39,152 --> 00:19:40,152
(Shy)

374
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:44,036
- Did you enjoy the breakfast?
- Yes, thanks to you.

375
00:19:44,444 --> 00:19:45,882
It was really good.

376
00:19:47,106 --> 00:19:48,883
- Are you a good cook?
- Nope.

377
00:19:48,908 --> 00:19:51,163
- Really?
- You seem to be a good cook.

378
00:19:51,188 --> 00:19:55,134
No, I'm just watching and copying others.

379
00:19:55,814 --> 00:19:57,417
Why do they look so good together?

380
00:19:57,442 --> 00:19:59,139
They must be overjoyed.
They're into each

381
00:19:59,164 --> 00:20:01,062
other, and they get to
do a couple photo shoot.

382
00:20:01,087 --> 00:20:03,207
And it was done randomly.

383
00:20:03,232 --> 00:20:04,868
- It's almost like fate.
- Fate. Exactly.

384
00:20:04,893 --> 00:20:06,543
(Destiny)

385
00:20:07,610 --> 00:20:10,317
- Ta-da.
- Wow, what's this?

386
00:20:10,342 --> 00:20:12,757
(Using a napkin, Won-jae
made a crane origami for In-seong.)

387
00:20:12,782 --> 00:20:16,092
- He made her a crane! Oh my!
- What the heck? So cute!

388
00:20:16,715 --> 00:20:18,279
Are we shooting outdoors?

389
00:20:19,004 --> 00:20:20,505
I think so.

390
00:20:20,530 --> 00:20:23,205
But with the nice weather,
it's fine to walk outside.

391
00:20:23,888 --> 00:20:26,637
- Right. - Even if we take it outdoors,
I think it will be pretty.

392
00:20:26,662 --> 00:20:30,021
- You're older, so speak casually to me.
- You can do the same, too.

393
00:20:30,111 --> 00:20:31,178
- Okay.
- Okay.

394
00:20:33,276 --> 00:20:35,813
(Paraspara Seoul)

395
00:20:35,838 --> 00:20:37,760
What do you want to
do if we get first place?

396
00:20:37,785 --> 00:20:41,144
(The five couples arrived at the location
where the challenge will take place.)

397
00:20:41,337 --> 00:20:43,504
- I'm nervous.
- Yeah, me, too.

398
00:20:43,537 --> 00:20:45,027
(What will happen today?)

399
00:20:45,052 --> 00:20:46,661
- Hello.
- Hello.

400
00:20:48,708 --> 00:20:52,356
(They get their key cards
and move to different places.)

401
00:20:52,381 --> 00:20:54,558
- It's over there.
- We each get a room?

402
00:20:55,276 --> 00:20:57,492
- Where are they?
- Where are they going?

403
00:20:57,693 --> 00:21:01,002
- Doesn't this look like a hobby?
- It seems like a hotel.

404
00:21:04,882 --> 00:21:07,365
(For some reason, they get nervous.)

405
00:21:07,390 --> 00:21:08,685
(Fan 1)

406
00:21:10,524 --> 00:21:12,055
It's suffocating.

407
00:21:12,341 --> 00:21:14,684
I'm losing my mind.
I'm so nervous.

408
00:21:15,243 --> 00:21:16,726
Gosh, what do we do?

409
00:21:17,737 --> 00:21:22,644
I wonder what kind of photo shoot
has been prepared this Tim. What is it?

410
00:21:23,608 --> 00:21:25,529
- I'm nervous.
- What will it be?

411
00:21:25,728 --> 00:21:27,578
Are there rose petals
scattered everywhere?

412
00:21:31,250 --> 00:21:34,387
- They each have their own room?
- They must be nervous.

413
00:21:36,225 --> 00:21:37,225
Oh my god!

414
00:21:37,520 --> 00:21:39,416
- Wait a minute.
- What's wrong?

415
00:21:40,967 --> 00:21:42,570
- What happened?
- What is it?

416
00:21:43,279 --> 00:21:44,374
It's very...

417
00:21:46,079 --> 00:21:47,559
Kinda sporty...

418
00:21:47,853 --> 00:21:48,853
Sporty?

419
00:21:50,344 --> 00:21:51,344
(Fake laugh)

420
00:21:53,140 --> 00:21:54,386
Wow, this is awesome.

421
00:21:55,007 --> 00:21:59,182
I can choose the combination
of what I want to wear?

422
00:22:00,052 --> 00:22:01,576
Oh, their outfits have been decided.

423
00:22:01,601 --> 00:22:03,141
The concepts are all different.

424
00:22:03,166 --> 00:22:04,712
(This?)

425
00:22:05,231 --> 00:22:06,231
(Fake laugh)

426
00:22:06,464 --> 00:22:10,090
I won't be able to look at you.
It'll be too uncomfortable.

427
00:22:10,944 --> 00:22:12,277
Isn't this too racy?

428
00:22:12,541 --> 00:22:14,469
- I think it's okay.
- THIS is okay?

429
00:22:14,494 --> 00:22:16,827
Well, I can pull if off if I have to.

430
00:22:17,141 --> 00:22:18,299
This is...

431
00:22:19,468 --> 00:22:23,747
I think we had the most shocking concept.

432
00:22:25,445 --> 00:22:26,715
There's a letter here.

433
00:22:26,954 --> 00:22:28,041
- Really?
- Yeah.

434
00:22:28,615 --> 00:22:30,681
- There's a card.
- Lemme see.

435
00:22:31,012 --> 00:22:32,012
Oh, what's that?

436
00:22:33,061 --> 00:22:35,864
- It's our concept. I see it.
- I'm nervous.

437
00:22:36,566 --> 00:22:37,700
What does it say?

438
00:22:45,114 --> 00:22:47,557
- "Wedding"?
- Their concept is wedding!

439
00:22:48,381 --> 00:22:51,151
"Please choose the outfit you will
wear for the today's photo shoot."

440
00:22:51,176 --> 00:22:53,295
Oh!

441
00:22:53,320 --> 00:22:55,670
They all have different concepts.

442
00:22:55,968 --> 00:22:58,684
"The tablet contains various
references about the photo shoot."

443
00:22:59,186 --> 00:23:00,939
- I guess it's in here.
- Yeah.

444
00:23:02,293 --> 00:23:05,461
(What kind of photos are in the tablet for
the couple with the wedding concept?)

445
00:23:06,661 --> 00:23:09,114
- Oh my god!
- It's too close!

446
00:23:09,459 --> 00:23:10,659
They're newlyweds.

447
00:23:11,117 --> 00:23:12,117
Hang on.

448
00:23:12,142 --> 00:23:14,857
At this rate, it could be seen as fate.

449
00:23:16,291 --> 00:23:17,616
Is there one you like?

450
00:23:18,754 --> 00:23:20,040
(Ta-da!)

451
00:23:20,494 --> 00:23:22,160
Can you even wear something like that?

452
00:23:23,576 --> 00:23:26,147
- It suddenly got hot.
- Oh my. Really?

453
00:23:29,208 --> 00:23:32,424
Wow. After this photo shoot,
their minds will change a lot.

454
00:23:33,850 --> 00:23:37,152
- We need to inject these
thoughts in our brain. - Right.

455
00:23:37,177 --> 00:23:40,615
We're really married, and we
came here for the wedding pictorial.

456
00:23:41,684 --> 00:23:44,763
"I love this person."

457
00:23:45,004 --> 00:23:46,171
Oh my goodness!

458
00:23:46,459 --> 00:23:49,424
Wow! If I were Jung-woo,
I would just ask her

459
00:23:49,449 --> 00:23:52,477
out before the day ends
and leave the program.

460
00:23:52,502 --> 00:23:53,828
I feel hot, too.

461
00:23:55,189 --> 00:23:56,641
He keeps fanning himself.

462
00:23:57,405 --> 00:23:59,135
(Su-won & Yeo-min: SUMMER)

463
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:01,257
- Their concept is "summer," right?
- Oh dear.

464
00:24:03,475 --> 00:24:04,475
I mean...

465
00:24:05,955 --> 00:24:07,661
Goodness. Let me take a look first.

466
00:24:07,971 --> 00:24:08,971
But...

467
00:24:10,503 --> 00:24:13,873
(Their concept's outfits
and poses are shocking.)

468
00:24:14,360 --> 00:24:15,820
It's unconventional.

469
00:24:16,362 --> 00:24:18,179
Should we look at the outfits?

470
00:24:18,523 --> 00:24:19,761
(Rummage)

471
00:24:20,812 --> 00:24:23,907
My clothes are standard.
You just have to decide.

472
00:24:24,348 --> 00:24:26,133
But like this...

473
00:24:26,158 --> 00:24:28,555
- This looks good.
- I think see-through styles are better.

474
00:24:29,693 --> 00:24:31,272
More than things like this.

475
00:24:31,297 --> 00:24:33,751
- I think this is the best one.
- This one?

476
00:24:33,913 --> 00:24:37,516
She's a professional.
It's like she's a real model.

477
00:24:38,156 --> 00:24:39,624
I think this is the best one.

478
00:24:39,894 --> 00:24:43,381
But if you get uncomfortable, it'll
make me more embarrassed, okay?

479
00:24:43,406 --> 00:24:44,406
Okay, okay.

480
00:24:45,809 --> 00:24:47,869
(Rough breathing
that fills the hallway...?)

481
00:24:47,894 --> 00:24:50,300
- What?
- What's going on?

482
00:24:54,490 --> 00:24:57,871
- Adorable! Who is that?
- Why does he always do the cutest things?

483
00:24:58,375 --> 00:24:59,375
|"Fit"?

484
00:24:59,401 --> 00:25:01,559
(A while ago in Won-jae
and In-seong's waiting room)

485
00:25:01,584 --> 00:25:04,465
(The two are deducing the concept)

486
00:25:05,040 --> 00:25:07,191
(Fitting? Fitness? Fit clothes Fit body?)

487
00:25:08,300 --> 00:25:10,696
- Is there a difference when you do that?
- Yes.

488
00:25:10,865 --> 00:25:12,690
It's totally different.

489
00:25:13,614 --> 00:25:15,653
- Let's spread these out.
- Okay.

490
00:25:15,678 --> 00:25:17,187
Let's put them on the bed.

491
00:25:17,212 --> 00:25:19,411
- You wanted to wear
something formal, right? - Yup.

492
00:25:20,010 --> 00:25:23,136
But not something matching like that.

493
00:25:23,584 --> 00:25:26,704
I want to wear this
with one of the jackets.

494
00:25:27,197 --> 00:25:28,991
