Look at my lips. I'll look at yours.

740
00:39:20,794 --> 00:39:22,405
Don't laugh. Don't laugh.

741
00:39:22,430 --> 00:39:26,027
If you kind of angle your body this way,
it'll be better. There you go! Fabulous!

742
00:39:28,160 --> 00:39:29,556
- There you go.
- Oh my god!

743
00:39:29,581 --> 00:39:31,867
- They're too close.
- They're really near each other.

744
00:39:34,164 --> 00:39:35,164
Oh my god.

745
00:39:35,303 --> 00:39:36,837
(Oh my. What do we do?)

746
00:39:38,535 --> 00:39:41,383
- What are you thinking about?
- I don't know.

747
00:39:41,408 --> 00:39:43,450
- Your mind is blank, huh?
- Yeah.

748
00:39:43,475 --> 00:39:46,756
Oh my goodness! "What
are you thinking about?"

749
00:39:46,781 --> 00:39:50,193
- He wasn't narrating it, right?
- Wow!

750
00:39:52,430 --> 00:39:54,358
- Are you looking at my lips?
- Yes.

751
00:39:58,197 --> 00:40:01,931
- Should we tilt our heads slightly?
- Like this? Okay.

752
00:40:02,602 --> 00:40:03,602
(Embarrassed)

753
00:40:03,833 --> 00:40:05,571
- Just until before they touch.
- Right.

754
00:40:05,596 --> 00:40:06,811
Wow, this is crazy!

755
00:40:12,492 --> 00:40:14,055
Wow! What's happening?

756
00:40:26,865 --> 00:40:29,882
- It's like a movie poster. They look
so good together. - Unbelievable!

757
00:40:29,907 --> 00:40:31,677
Wow, this is seriously first place.

758
00:40:33,363 --> 00:40:35,546
- I bet this is the winner!
- Me, too.

759
00:40:35,571 --> 00:40:37,406
- Doesn't it steal your breath away?
- Yeah!

760
00:40:37,613 --> 00:40:40,321
Maybe it's 'cause we saw the
process, but just this makes us go...

761
00:40:40,346 --> 00:40:41,713
(Goosebumps)

762
00:40:41,738 --> 00:40:46,719
Just by looking at their picture, you
can hear the words they exchanged.

763
00:40:46,744 --> 00:40:50,203
And the way Ha-neul's fingers
moved as if she didn't know what to do.

764
00:40:50,228 --> 00:40:52,190
That made me shake!

765
00:40:52,215 --> 00:40:56,958
- First off, Yeo-min was really cool.
- Right.

766
00:40:56,983 --> 00:41:00,239
- The way Su-won looked at
her was like... - "We have to win."

767
00:41:00,264 --> 00:41:04,281
Exactly. "We're going to win."

768
00:41:04,787 --> 00:41:07,398
Honestly, Won-jae and
In-seong's couple photos...

769
00:41:07,423 --> 00:41:09,684
- They were incredible.
- Don't they look good together?

770
00:41:09,709 --> 00:41:13,734
In-seong shows great
chemistry with younger guys.

771
00:41:13,896 --> 00:41:19,780
But Da-Na and Jung-woo's
pictorial really made hearts flutter, too.

772
00:41:19,805 --> 00:41:22,835
I pick Ji-min and Ha-neul.

773
00:41:22,860 --> 00:41:24,303
- Me, too.
- Me, three.

774
00:41:24,407 --> 00:41:27,408
- Just looking at them made my
heart race. - I know.

775
00:41:29,036 --> 00:41:33,714
(Raindrops are falling
over the Love Mansion.)

776
00:41:34,967 --> 00:41:37,355
- I liked our concept.
- Yeah!

777
00:41:37,380 --> 00:41:43,216
(The five couples are walking
together while sharing umbrellas.)

778
00:41:44,516 --> 00:41:45,793
Our photos!

779
00:41:46,105 --> 00:41:47,867
Oh my god! I can't look! What do I do?

780
00:41:50,340 --> 00:41:53,484
(Five photos are in the front
yard of the Love Mansion.)

781
00:41:53,509 --> 00:41:56,129
- Everyone really went all out.
- Seriously.

782
00:41:56,371 --> 00:41:57,632
Whoa, what's that?

783
00:41:58,426 --> 00:41:59,893
Let's go a bit closer.

784
00:42:00,794 --> 00:42:02,225
(Grab)

785
00:42:02,250 --> 00:42:03,424
(Linking arms/Squeeze)

786
00:42:03,449 --> 00:42:05,997
- Oh my word.
- They held hands?

787
00:42:06,667 --> 00:42:08,267
This is so entertaining!

788
00:42:08,923 --> 00:42:10,280
That one's awesome.

789
00:42:10,733 --> 00:42:11,800
It's the winner.

790
00:42:12,371 --> 00:42:13,783
Did we go all out?

791
00:42:14,547 --> 00:42:16,547
They really look like newlyweds.

792
00:42:17,606 --> 00:42:20,837
- Are you cold? I'll give you this.
- Oh my.

793
00:42:21,356 --> 00:42:24,943
- This one looks great.
- So cute.

794
00:42:25,281 --> 00:42:27,162
You could probably hear his heartbeat.

795
00:42:27,656 --> 00:42:29,704
- The mood came out nicely, huh?
- Yeah.

796
00:42:30,722 --> 00:42:34,724
- It came out really nicely.
- I really wanna hide!

797
00:42:34,981 --> 00:42:36,457
Wow, this is crazy.

798
00:42:37,065 --> 00:42:41,256
We'll tell you some comments about how
we felt about these pictures in this order.

799
00:42:41,281 --> 00:42:43,234
We'll share some comments.

800
00:42:43,397 --> 00:42:46,095
We'll talk about this one first.

801
00:42:46,456 --> 00:42:50,697
They made a lot of preparations
and smiled so wonderfully.

802
00:42:50,722 --> 00:42:53,173
So they really gave off newlywed vibes.

803
00:42:53,198 --> 00:42:57,844
We were shocked that they would laugh so
brightly when they were using honorifics.

804
00:42:57,869 --> 00:43:00,042
One thing we thought
was regrettable was that

805
00:43:00,067 --> 00:43:02,287
Jung-woo had a hard
time looking at the camera.

806
00:43:02,312 --> 00:43:04,986
So it was a bit awkward for Da-Na.

807
00:43:05,275 --> 00:43:08,170
Besides that, they did a splendid job.

808
00:43:08,811 --> 00:43:14,144
The two of them were very proactive.

809
00:43:14,521 --> 00:43:18,816
They made so much efforts that we
didn't have to really give them any advice.

810
00:43:19,147 --> 00:43:22,249
So we were able to quickly
produce professional photos.

811
00:43:22,281 --> 00:43:25,539
They were really proactive.
That left a deep impression.

812
00:43:27,052 --> 00:43:28,694
- Wow.
- Thank you.

813
00:43:29,252 --> 00:43:33,667
- And the next photo... - It really felt
like a professional photo shoot.

814
00:43:33,829 --> 00:43:36,694
Their gazes suddenly changed.

815
00:43:36,719 --> 00:43:40,649
It must have been difficult, but
they followed our lead really well.

816
00:43:40,674 --> 00:43:41,674
Thank you.

817
00:43:41,986 --> 00:43:45,821
For the next couple, we aimed
for something sporty and cute.

818
00:43:46,049 --> 00:43:50,326
At first, they were awkward,
but as time went on...

819
00:43:50,386 --> 00:43:52,187
We could feel them getting energized.

820
00:43:52,212 --> 00:43:56,213
And that was adorably
depicted in the photos.

821
00:43:56,408 --> 00:43:59,675
- And this was from our last photo shoot.
- Yes.

822
00:43:59,700 --> 00:44:03,602
While taking their photos, I
could feel the slight tension.

823
00:44:04,076 --> 00:44:05,312
Their tension.

824
00:44:05,672 --> 00:44:10,005
That made the photo sexier.

825
00:44:15,373 --> 00:44:16,573
Oh my god, Su-won.

826
00:44:18,255 --> 00:44:21,366
- He's gonna pierce a hole in there!
- His eyes are burning!

827
00:44:21,483 --> 00:44:23,553
I think he could kill
Ji-min with his glare.

828
00:44:23,954 --> 00:44:25,564
We are now going to announce the winner.

829
00:44:25,765 --> 00:44:29,134
Before that, I want to let you
know that the winners will have

830
00:44:29,270 --> 00:44:32,387
the chance to go on a night
date with someone of their choice.

831
00:44:35,426 --> 00:44:38,775
It took us a while to pick the
winner, and we'll reveal it now.

832
00:44:39,929 --> 00:44:42,874
The first place of today's challenge is...

833
00:44:44,514 --> 00:44:46,268
Everyone really came out nicely.

834
00:44:46,835 --> 00:44:49,732
(Which couple will get
to go on night dates?)

835
00:44:49,757 --> 00:44:50,757
The winners are...

836
00:44:51,097 --> 00:44:54,140
- Lee Yeo-min.
- And Jung Su-won.

837
00:44:54,165 --> 00:44:56,507
- Thank you!
- Congrats!

838
00:44:56,532 --> 00:44:57,532
Oh, Su-won?

839
00:44:59,775 --> 00:45:01,665
- Congratulations.
- Congrats!

840
00:45:02,605 --> 00:45:04,144
It can't be helped.

841
00:45:04,795 --> 00:45:06,495
- So cool.
- Thank you.

842
00:45:06,520 --> 00:45:08,140
Thank you!

843
00:45:09,134 --> 00:45:11,983
They were truly professionals.

844
00:45:12,481 --> 00:45:16,203
The winning couple isn't going
on a date with each other, right?

845
00:45:16,397 --> 00:45:21,449
They could. It's their choice.
They each get to choose their dates.

846
00:45:21,587 --> 00:45:26,102
If they choose to go on
dates with different people,

847
00:45:26,507 --> 00:45:28,327
then they really had a
business relationship.

848
00:45:28,886 --> 00:45:31,538
They're professionals. I
wonder how Yeo-min feels.

849
00:45:35,880 --> 00:45:41,592
(The screen suddenly turned on.)

850
00:45:43,680 --> 00:45:48,808
(The winners of the challenge
can choose their dates.)

851
00:45:49,125 --> 00:45:51,256
What should I do? I
have a lot on my mind.

852
00:45:52,561 --> 00:45:54,418
Who will she go with?

853
00:45:55,287 --> 00:45:57,954
Should I pick someone I'm interested in?

854
00:45:58,637 --> 00:46:01,450
Or someone I've never really talked to?

855
00:46:03,781 --> 00:46:05,368
- Enjoy it.
- Enjoy it.

856
00:46:07,801 --> 00:46:08,983
The winner has to choose!

857
00:46:11,480 --> 00:46:14,900
So this would be an official
first date where they get to go out.

858
00:46:16,064 --> 00:46:20,444
I want to go on a date
with Ha-neul the most.

859
00:46:24,428 --> 00:46:27,111
(Su-won chooses Ha-neul without hesitation)

860
00:46:27,136 --> 00:46:30,313
- He's straightforward. He didn't
even think about it. - He just did it.

861
00:46:31,780 --> 00:46:35,515
(Yeo-min appears afterward.)

862
00:46:35,942 --> 00:46:37,315
Gosh, I'm really curious.

863
00:46:40,101 --> 00:46:42,080
Who will she choose?

864
00:46:45,053 --> 00:46:49,730
(Out of the five guys, who
does Yeo-min want to be with?)

865
00:46:50,156 --> 00:46:52,446
I chose him because I
wanted to spend time with

866
00:46:52,471 --> 00:46:54,808
someone I couldn't have
a deep conversation with.

867
00:46:58,098 --> 00:47:00,098
Who is it? Who did she choose?

868
00:47:01,087 --> 00:47:02,928
It's unpredictable.

869
00:47:03,394 --> 00:47:06,224
(Women's lodging)

870
00:47:06,999 --> 00:47:08,570
What's with your expression?

871
00:47:09,347 --> 00:47:10,500
Are you tired?

872
00:47:12,316 --> 00:47:13,781
Is there a lot on your mind?

873
00:47:14,514 --> 00:47:17,419
- She looks troubled.
- She seems to have a lot on her mind.

874
00:47:19,997 --> 00:47:22,981
You already decided.
So just enjoy it.

875
00:47:27,580 --> 00:47:30,012
(In the middle of Yeo-min's
thoughts, the screen turns on.)

876
00:47:30,577 --> 00:47:31,808
(Startled)

877
00:47:32,086 --> 00:47:33,086
Oh, what's going on?

878
00:47:40,046 --> 00:47:42,287
(Night Date Couples)

879
00:47:42,312 --> 00:47:44,440
They're revealing it to everyone?

880
00:47:45,412 --> 00:47:47,269
So they're revealing it like this.

881
00:47:47,650 --> 00:47:49,007
(Curious)

882
00:47:49,280 --> 00:47:50,899
Whoa, I'm curious!

883
00:47:51,330 --> 00:47:52,623
(Smile)

884
00:47:54,051 --> 00:47:57,143
(What is Yeo-min's choice that will
make someone happy and someone sad?)

885
00:48:00,550 --> 00:48:02,116
She chose Jung-woo?

886
00:48:02,588 --> 00:48:04,159
- Out of the blue?
- That's unexpected.

887
00:48:04,184 --> 00:48:06,384
- Jung-woo, huh?
- He's popular.

888
00:48:06,409 --> 00:48:07,409
I know.

889
00:48:10,224 --> 00:48:11,224
What?

890
00:48:12,075 --> 00:48:13,608
Wow, that's unexpected!

891
00:48:15,014 --> 00:48:16,948
Huh? Me? I was going to rest.

892
00:48:20,488 --> 00:48:22,100
She feels bad.

893
00:48:30,601 --> 00:48:33,516
- But actually, she doesn't need
to feel bad. - Right!

894
00:48:33,541 --> 00:48:35,613
There's a chance for everyone.

895
00:48:36,983 --> 00:48:39,824
(Jung Su-won -> Lee Ha-neul
Another couple going on a night date)

896
00:48:40,473 --> 00:48:42,883
(Does she feel the same way about him?)

897
00:48:47,874 --> 00:48:53,021
(Before the night grows
deeper, they leave for their dates.)

898
00:48:53,046 --> 00:48:55,579
- Dates?
- They're leaving right away.

899
00:48:56,549 --> 00:48:58,574
(She can't hide her smile.)

900
00:49:02,998 --> 00:49:06,035
(With an umbrella, Su-won
comes to get Ha-neul.)

901
00:49:08,118 --> 00:49:09,384
(She spots Su-won.)

902
00:49:14,011 --> 00:49:15,289
(Tickle, tickle)

903
00:49:15,728 --> 00:49:16,728
I'll be back.

904
00:49:16,944 --> 00:49:19,335
- Bye! Have fun!
- Why am I more excited?

905
00:49:19,360 --> 00:49:20,622
Way to go!

906
00:49:22,785 --> 00:49:24,069
See you!

907
00:49:27,289 --> 00:49:30,273
- I didn't know I would pick you up
when everyone's there. - Me neither.

908
00:49:30,583 --> 00:49:32,069
I was shocked.

909
00:49:32,825 --> 00:49:34,970
What are they gonna do? I'm so curious!

910
00:49:36,399 --> 00:49:38,378
Why is my heart flutter?

911
00:49:40,088 --> 00:49:42,217
I was thinking about it and...

912
00:49:42,242 --> 00:49:46,869
(He hides his embarrassment
with light jokes.)

913
00:49:50,512 --> 00:49:51,861
Yeo-min is going out, too.

914
00:49:52,221 --> 00:49:54,585
- It's their first date outside
the Love Mansion. - Yeah.

915
00:49:55,565 --> 00:49:57,073
(Men's lodging)

916
00:49:57,098 --> 00:49:58,361
Is that Won-jae?

917
00:49:59,305 --> 00:50:00,305
It's Jung-woo.

918
00:50:00,330 --> 00:50:02,903
- Are they doing another photo shoot?
- Why is he working out?

919
00:50:04,678 --> 00:50:06,078
I guess he's nervous.

920
00:50:06,949 --> 00:50:09,101
(Yeo-min walks towards Jung-woo first.)

921
00:50:12,955 --> 00:50:14,130
(Knock, knock)

922
00:50:15,262 --> 00:50:16,690
Jung-woo.

923
00:50:21,126 --> 00:50:22,793
(Pretending to be asleep)

924
00:50:23,539 --> 00:50:25,587
- I'll be back.
- Have fun.

925
00:50:27,543 --> 00:50:30,067
- Bye.
- Aww, Won-jae.

926
00:50:30,707 --> 00:50:31,707
Goodness.

927
00:50:32,634 --> 00:50:34,034
I didn't expect this.

928
00:50:34,710 --> 00:50:36,976
- Why? You don't like it?
- I do.

929
00:50:37,888 --> 00:50:43,724
They checked their interest in each
other but she chose someone else.)

930
00:50:44,292 --> 00:50:49,125
- I think he thought she'd choose him.
- Yeah.

931
00:50:56,058 --> 00:50:58,224
I interrupted your free time.

932
00:50:58,306 --> 00:50:59,719
- No, this is great.
- Really?

933
00:50:59,744 --> 00:51:01,314
- Yup.
- You said it's unexpected.

934
00:51:01,858 --> 00:51:03,256
It's really unexpected.

935
00:51:04,453 --> 00:51:07,526
I just thought it was too bad that
we couldn't talk on the first day.

936
00:51:08,204 --> 00:51:10,547
- We didn't have time the next day either.
- Right.

937
00:51:10,572 --> 00:51:12,414
Right? It was chaotic.

938
00:51:13,021 --> 00:51:18,973
And we spent a lot of time
with only one person today, too.

939
00:51:20,504 --> 00:51:22,702
I did want to talk with you, too.

940
00:51:22,727 --> 00:51:23,860
- Right?
- Yeah.

941
00:51:23,885 --> 00:51:25,198
- Oh, you mean it?
- Yup.

942
00:51:27,941 --> 00:51:30,092
- Your photos came out nicely.
- Really?

943
00:51:30,117 --> 00:51:31,450
- Yours, too.
- Me?

944
00:51:31,475 --> 00:51:33,151
You guys were like newlyweds.

945
00:51:33,789 --> 00:51:35,989
I kind of felt bad towards Da-an.

946
00:51:36,535 --> 00:51:37,535
Why?

947
00:51:37,981 --> 00:51:41,197
She did a great job,
but I spoiled the photos.

948
00:51:41,222 --> 00:51:43,822
No, you two were really like newlyweds.

949
00:51:45,387 --> 00:51:48,212
You really looked like a new
husband. You did a fantastic job.

950
00:51:49,639 --> 00:51:51,599
- I mean it.
- You were like a model, too.

951
00:51:54,088 --> 00:51:55,675
They're exchanging praises.

952
00:51:55,700 --> 00:51:56,865
They're going back and forth.

953
00:51:56,890 --> 00:52:00,290
- Jung-woo looks good with anyone.
- You're right.

954
00:52:00,543 --> 00:52:02,188
He has good chemistry with everyone.

955
00:52:04,941 --> 00:52:08,639
- Did you check the locker yesterday?
- Yeah.

956
00:52:09,097 --> 00:52:11,199
How was it? Did you get a lot of coins?

957
00:52:11,726 --> 00:52:14,662
- Nope.
- Really? Why not?

958
00:52:15,057 --> 00:52:19,912
(Last night, Ha-neul confirmed
that she got two Love Coins.)

959
00:52:22,389 --> 00:52:24,809
I thought I wouldn't get any coins.

960
00:52:27,699 --> 00:52:31,894
(They exchanged Love Coins, but she
didn't choose him for the dinner date.)

961
00:52:32,485 --> 00:52:35,987
(He didn't expect it, but there
was one Love Coin in his locker.)

962
00:52:36,347 --> 00:52:37,450
I guess you got a coin.

963
00:52:39,110 --> 00:52:40,706
Didn't you give it to me?

964
00:52:41,534 --> 00:52:43,755
- Who knows?
- I think it's from you.

965
00:52:45,070 --> 00:52:49,182
So I assumed it was you
and chose you for this date.

966
00:52:53,191 --> 00:52:55,000
You said you didn't know who to choose.

967
00:52:55,025 --> 00:52:57,516
That's because of what you did yesterday.

968
00:52:57,870 --> 00:53:00,187
- You checked the votes after
the dinner date. - What?

969
00:53:00,705 --> 00:53:02,905
Right. That's why I was relieved.

970
00:53:05,605 --> 00:53:07,795
So I was able to go
comfortably back to the room.

971
00:53:10,817 --> 00:53:13,206
How was it being with
Yeo-min the whole day?

972
00:53:14,011 --> 00:53:16,796
Well, it was fun,

973
00:53:17,562 --> 00:53:22,625
but I wasn't really attracted to her.

974
00:53:23,386 --> 00:53:26,711
I'm the type to go after only one girl.

975
00:53:27,896 --> 00:53:30,945
Like a pro. Well, I'm not a pro,
but I want to go forward like one.

976
00:53:30,970 --> 00:53:35,116
But you guys posed
like that in those outfits.

977
00:53:35,510 --> 00:53:40,748
That's how I was able to
confirm my feelings even more.

978
00:53:41,024 --> 00:53:42,809
Despite all that,

979
00:53:43,406 --> 00:53:50,251
I realized that it didn't make
me have feelings for her.

980
00:53:50,812 --> 00:53:53,546
- So Ha-neul was concerned, too.
- Yeah.

981
00:53:54,085 --> 00:53:55,568
So how was it for you?

982
00:53:57,544 --> 00:54:01,406
In the selected photo, you couldn't
see it, but my outfit was pretty revealing.

983
00:54:01,431 --> 00:54:03,823
I see. But I'm not talking
about the photo shoot.

984
00:54:04,151 --> 00:54:05,770
- How was it with Ji-min?
- Yeah.

985
00:54:05,795 --> 00:54:06,979
That's what I want to know.

986
00:54:07,004 --> 00:54:09,971
It doesn't matter what you
did during the photo shoot.

987
00:54:10,927 --> 00:54:12,681
- He's comfortable to be around.
- Really?

988
00:54:12,706 --> 00:54:16,073
- Then again, Ji-min is...
- He's super sweet.

989
00:54:17,634 --> 00:54:19,070
His expression changed right away.

990
00:54:20,041 --> 00:54:23,307
He takes good care of
me and talks with me a lot.

991
00:54:24,783 --> 00:54:27,315
Okay. I see.

992
00:54:28,471 --> 00:54:30,582
His expression quickly darkened.

993
00:54:30,607 --> 00:54:32,172
But Ji-min said this.

994
00:54:33,172 --> 00:54:37,231
"I'm a man, too."

995
00:54:37,734 --> 00:54:39,067
- Really?
- Yeah.

996
00:54:39,425 --> 00:54:42,227
I wondered if I treated him too casually.

997
00:54:43,598 --> 00:54:44,598
He hates it.

998
00:54:44,670 --> 00:54:47,297
He really can't hide how he feels.

999
00:54:47,412 --> 00:54:51,443
Why do you think she said that?
What if you were in her shoes?

1000
00:54:52,121 --> 00:54:53,652
"I'm a man, too."

1001
00:54:54,440 --> 00:54:56,410
(There are lots to say,
but I won't say them.)

1002
00:54:57,676 --> 00:54:59,890
Or it could be a plan to
make the other person jealous.

1003
00:54:59,915 --> 00:55:04,067
That's true because he's
transparent about his feelings like that,

1004
00:55:04,091 --> 00:55:07,429
so I don't think she
didn't notice it at all.

1005
00:55:10,194 --> 00:55:12,768
(Like someone's heart, the
raindrops fall hopelessly.)

1006
00:55:13,852 --> 00:55:18,170
- They're the ones who didn't get chosen.
- It's raining, too.

1007
00:55:22,433 --> 00:55:24,500
Jae-hyung must be really tired.

1008
00:55:25,657 --> 00:55:27,633
- He woke up at dawn.
- He woke up at 6 a.m.

1009
00:55:28,756 --> 00:55:29,885
That's right.

1010
00:55:29,910 --> 00:55:31,977
He must be exhausted.
What's the use of getting

1011
00:55:32,002 --> 00:55:34,155
his Lamborghini? He has
no chances with the women.

1012
00:55:39,490 --> 00:55:40,680
(Spring)

1013
00:55:41,419 --> 00:55:42,950
(Spring 2)

1014
00:55:44,217 --> 00:55:46,416
Is it right for us to
just lie here like this?

1015
00:55:47,499 --> 00:55:49,420
You want to go to the kitchen?

1016
00:55:49,883 --> 00:55:52,907
- No, I just want to say something.
- Oh, so you want me to tag along?

1017
00:55:54,220 --> 00:55:56,775
- No, that's a bit strange.
- Okay, then go ahead.

1018
00:56:01,335 --> 00:56:02,735
(Knock, knock, knock)

1019
00:56:03,610 --> 00:56:05,199
I think that's hard to do.

1020
00:56:06,319 --> 00:56:08,947
(It's a visit that's as difficult as
knocking on someone's heart.)

1021
00:56:08,972 --> 00:56:12,204
- It seems like Ji-min has
something to say. - To who?

1022
00:56:14,782 --> 00:56:17,186
Is he going to Ji-min?

1023
00:56:18,361 --> 00:56:20,896
- That's possible.
- Yeah. If it's not Ha-neul, it's...

1024
00:56:20,921 --> 00:56:21,921
Precisely.

1025
00:56:25,492 --> 00:56:27,342
(He musters up the
courage and takes a peek.)

1026
00:56:27,367 --> 00:56:28,367
(It's empty.)

1027
00:56:28,392 --> 00:56:30,138
- No one's here.
- Where did they go?

1028
00:56:31,077 --> 00:56:32,275
No one's there.

1029
00:56:32,676 --> 00:56:34,731
Gosh, he mustered the
courage to come here though.

1030
00:56:36,355 --> 00:56:39,250
(In the meantime, Da-Na heads somewhere.)

1031
00:56:39,275 --> 00:56:43,039
(Room of Expressing Interests)

1032
00:56:47,248 --> 00:56:50,278
(She carefully opens the door.)

1033
00:56:53,632 --> 00:56:56,284
- She came to choose.
- Who will she give it to?

1034
00:57:00,257 --> 00:57:05,252
(Who will she give her first coin to?)

1035
00:57:05,277 --> 00:57:06,277
Who can it be?

1036
00:57:09,005 --> 00:57:10,521
There's already one in there!

1037
00:57:11,604 --> 00:57:12,604
Two coins?

1038
00:57:13,383 --> 00:57:16,288
(Who is it...?)

1039
00:57:21,343 --> 00:57:22,820
(Appears)

1040
00:57:26,835 --> 00:57:28,168
There's no one here.

1041
00:57:29,855 --> 00:57:30,974
Oh? What are you doing?

1042
00:57:30,999 --> 00:57:32,681
- The girls aren't in their room.
- Yeah.

1043
00:57:32,706 --> 00:57:34,667
- Where did they go?
- Oh, they're washing up.

1044
00:57:34,692 --> 00:57:36,836
- Oh, really? Already?
- Yes.

1045
00:57:36,861 --> 00:57:38,045
What are the guys doing?

1046
00:57:38,070 --> 00:57:40,094
We're tired, so we're just resting.

1047
00:57:40,119 --> 00:57:42,112
- I see.
- Do you wanna talk for a bit?

1048
00:57:43,103 --> 00:57:44,360
(Thinking)

1049
00:57:44,672 --> 00:57:45,997
- Should we?
- Oh my god.

1050
00:57:46,556 --> 00:57:47,572
Wow, that means...

1051
00:57:47,597 --> 00:57:50,476
In the middle of their conversation,
he'll tell Da-Na, "I'm a man, too!"

1052
00:57:51,830 --> 00:57:52,830
Again?

1053
00:57:52,997 --> 00:57:54,545
It's like his self-introduction.

1054
00:57:58,663 --> 00:58:00,353
- Did you get used to everything?
- Me?

1055
00:58:00,984 --> 00:58:02,784
It's better than yesterday.

1056
00:58:02,915 --> 00:58:05,081
You seem brighter than expected.

1057
00:58:05,106 --> 00:58:06,106
- Me?
- Yes.

1058
00:58:06,830 --> 00:58:09,958
I am, but people don't really
know me, so it's awkward.

1059
00:58:09,983 --> 00:58:13,667
When we first met, I noticed
you were being careful.

1060
00:58:13,692 --> 00:58:15,004
Oh, really?

1061
00:58:15,426 --> 00:58:18,792
- I thought you might be uncomfortable.
- That day was really...

1062
00:58:20,360 --> 00:58:22,098
- Hello.
- Hey.

1063
00:58:24,751 --> 00:58:26,100
(Glance)

1064
00:58:27,884 --> 00:58:29,931
- It's Won-jae.
- Won-jae.

1065
00:58:31,103 --> 00:58:32,840
How is it? Are you having fun?

1066
00:58:33,534 --> 00:58:37,033
- It's been three days, right?
- Right.

1067
00:58:37,207 --> 00:58:39,592
- We're curious what you think.
- Oh, me?

1068
00:58:40,144 --> 00:58:42,263
It feels like I barely
adjusted to everything today.

1069
00:58:42,512 --> 00:58:44,869
Do you have any clues about
what the people here are like?

1070
00:58:44,894 --> 00:58:49,545
- For the guys, besides Jung-woo,
I haven't... - Talked to them?

1071
00:58:49,570 --> 00:58:51,367
I haven't spoken to them yet.

1072
00:58:51,392 --> 00:58:53,037
There was no chance.

1073
00:58:53,182 --> 00:58:58,071
We feel the same way. We want
to talk, but there's no chance to.

1074
00:58:59,623 --> 00:59:00,623
(Smile)

1075
00:59:06,051 --> 00:59:08,028
Should I go call the girls?

1076
00:59:09,866 --> 00:59:12,666
I guess neither of them got her Love Coin.

1077
00:59:13,504 --> 00:59:16,090
- Sure. - I think they'll be
lounging around anyway.

1078
00:59:17,349 --> 00:59:19,984
(Da-Na leaves for a second.)

1079
00:59:22,059 --> 00:59:24,789
- She must've been uncomfortable.
- I'm sure she was.

1080
00:59:26,821 --> 00:59:31,260
The guys are waiting for us.

1081
00:59:31,285 --> 00:59:33,546
- Why?
- Just to talk.

1082
00:59:33,571 --> 00:59:36,849
- Oh, really?
- So I said I'd bring you guys.

1083
00:59:37,410 --> 00:59:39,259
- It's awkward by yourself, huh?
- Yeah.

1084
00:59:39,284 --> 00:59:43,412
If we don't go, it'll
be like I ditched them.

1085
00:59:43,436 --> 00:59:46,059
No. I'll be right there.

1086
00:59:46,084 --> 00:59:47,084
Okay.

1087
00:59:47,811 --> 00:59:50,629
Ji-min, how do you feel?
Are you still set on the same person?

1088
00:59:50,654 --> 00:59:52,987
Me? Did I ever tell you about my feelings?

1089
00:59:54,095 --> 00:59:55,095
Well...

1090
00:59:55,857 --> 00:59:58,124
Any guesses who I'm interested in?

1091
00:59:58,465 --> 01:00:03,155
Well, even if I don't, I just want
to know if you changed your mind or not.

1092
01:00:04,692 --> 01:00:06,661
Yes, they should slowly
start talking about that.

1093
01:00:07,299 --> 01:00:10,141
- I...
- He's here.

1094
01:00:11,130 --> 01:00:12,130
You scared me.

1095
01:00:13,465 --> 01:00:16,908
(Jae-hyung appeared out of curiosity.)

1096
01:00:17,088 --> 01:00:19,889
If we're talking about
who I want to get to know...

1097
01:00:23,539 --> 01:00:24,959
There are about two of them.

1098
01:00:26,363 --> 01:00:27,363
(Intrigued)

1099
01:00:27,388 --> 01:00:29,122
But I can't say it hastily.

1100
01:00:31,460 --> 01:00:32,460
What about you?

1101
01:00:33,833 --> 01:00:34,833
I...

1102
01:00:35,742 --> 01:00:38,876
(The two of them are
honestly sharing their feelings.)

1103
01:00:39,008 --> 01:00:42,206
After spending three days here, there's
someone who matches my ideal type.

1104
01:00:42,231 --> 01:00:43,359
- Really?
- Yeah.

1105
01:00:43,384 --> 01:00:44,932
I see. You realized that today?

1106
01:00:45,610 --> 01:00:46,610
Yeah.

1107
01:00:47,946 --> 01:00:50,684
I really want to know who she is.
But I won't ask.

1108
01:00:54,083 --> 01:00:55,777
I think it could be In-seong.

1109
01:00:55,802 --> 01:00:58,446
- During their photo shoot.
- He did say he realized it today.

1110
01:00:58,957 --> 01:01:01,116
- I'm back.
- Should we have a drink?

1111
01:01:01,705 --> 01:01:02,705
(Cheers.)

1112
01:01:03,533 --> 01:01:04,834
Gosh, it's good.

1113
01:01:05,115 --> 01:01:08,273
You don't drink?

1114
01:01:08,713 --> 01:01:10,379
Me? Do you like to drink?

1115
01:01:12,028 --> 01:01:13,684
(Failed to hold
in their laughter)

1116
01:01:13,709 --> 01:01:17,251
What's wrong with him? He turns weird
if there's at least three people around!

1117
01:01:17,667 --> 01:01:19,714
It's like he's here to hook
people up at the club.

1118
01:01:20,557 --> 01:01:23,337
I've never seen his
eyes that big before.

1119
01:01:24,421 --> 01:01:25,699
You don't drink?

1120
01:01:26,089 --> 01:01:27,962
Me? Do you like to drink?

1121
01:01:28,884 --> 01:01:30,218
- Yes.
- Really?

1122
01:01:30,243 --> 01:01:31,243
I don't dislike it.

1123
01:01:32,515 --> 01:01:35,184
I don't like alcohol, but
it depends on the mood.

1124
01:01:39,429 --> 01:01:43,067
- Did you adjust to everything?
- More than yesterday.

1125
01:01:44,847 --> 01:01:46,831
It seems like you've adjusted quite a lot.

1126
01:01:47,533 --> 01:01:51,501
I actually didn't say a
word on the first day.

1127
01:01:51,773 --> 01:01:55,576
- Why not?
- It was awkward for me at first, too.

1128
01:01:57,145 --> 01:02:02,939
On the first day, I wasn't in a situation
where I was interested in anyone.

1129
01:02:03,526 --> 01:02:07,057
But Da-Na is the closest to that.

1130
01:02:07,824 --> 01:02:12,414
I didn't talk much with her yet,
but all possibilities are open.

1131
01:02:13,798 --> 01:02:15,942
I've gotten a bit more relaxed.

1132
01:02:16,326 --> 01:02:18,230
- Hello.
- You're here!

1133
01:02:18,255 --> 01:02:19,969
- Hey.
- You look refreshed.

1134
01:02:19,994 --> 01:02:23,725
I feel... so much better now.

1135
01:02:23,750 --> 01:02:26,761
What do you think they're doing
on their dates? Aren't you curious?

1136
01:02:26,939 --> 01:02:29,597
Come to think of it, we weren't
thinking about that at all.

1137
01:02:29,622 --> 01:02:31,116
What are they doing on their dates?

1138
01:02:31,141 --> 01:02:34,063
Weren't you curious? The girls always were.

1139
01:02:34,517 --> 01:02:36,089
- I'm dying of curiosity.
- Same.

1140
01:02:38,079 --> 01:02:39,912
It's amazing. I'm glad we came out.

1141
01:02:41,113 --> 01:02:44,050
- Oh, can we look at that, too?
- Which one?

1142
01:02:44,075 --> 01:02:46,369
Up there where the telescope is?

1143
01:02:47,182 --> 01:02:48,912
- Should we go?
- Yeah!

1144
01:02:49,634 --> 01:02:53,662
(Bugak Skyway)

1145
01:02:53,687 --> 01:02:56,309
It's cool. I like it.

1146
01:02:56,695 --> 01:02:59,557
I feel like we entered the fog.

1147
01:02:59,887 --> 01:03:01,942
Will we be able to see the night view?

1148
01:03:02,833 --> 01:03:04,659
- You can look at it now.
- Really?

1149
01:03:06,188 --> 01:03:08,315
It's just blurry to me.

1150
01:03:08,496 --> 01:03:10,029
Try to make it clearer.

1151
01:03:10,054 --> 01:03:11,054
How?

1152
01:03:13,249 --> 01:03:14,582
I don't see anything.

1153
01:03:15,193 --> 01:03:16,527
This isn't much fog.

1154
01:03:17,211 --> 01:03:19,306
We can still see the view? Really?

1155
01:03:20,436 --> 01:03:23,580
- It's enough to just look at it
with our eyes. - Yeah.

1156
01:03:25,492 --> 01:03:27,246
It doesn't matter if
they can see it or not.

1157
01:03:27,271 --> 01:03:29,338
That's not what's important right now.

1158
01:03:33,961 --> 01:03:37,373
Should we speak casually to each other?

1159
01:03:40,833 --> 01:03:42,952
- You're good at that.
- At what?

1160
01:03:42,977 --> 01:03:45,796
- I'm pretty sociable, too.
- I see.

1161
01:03:46,499 --> 01:03:48,625
- But you're better than me.
- That's because I drank.

1162
01:03:48,650 --> 01:03:51,420
I don't think so. I can tell by
talking with you a couple times.

1163
01:03:52,179 --> 01:03:55,194
Sure, let's speak casually.
Ji-min, you can drop the honorifics, too.

1164
01:03:56,538 --> 01:03:57,538
Alright.

1165
01:03:59,508 --> 01:04:00,508
So adorable!

1166
01:04:01,215 --> 01:04:02,215
(Frozen)

1167
01:04:02,240 --> 01:04:03,240
Alright.

1168
01:04:03,714 --> 01:04:06,247
You just drew a firm line, didn't you?

1169
01:04:07,241 --> 01:04:10,353
She's never going to drop the
honorifics with you. Not in her lifetime.

1170
01:04:10,378 --> 01:04:13,921
- So we're going to speak casually now?
- Yeah, casually.

1171
01:04:14,481 --> 01:04:16,547
- Should we do the same?
- No.

1172
01:04:18,977 --> 01:04:20,333
Oh, should we play a game?

1173
01:04:21,456 --> 01:04:22,456
A board game?

1174
01:04:22,608 --> 01:04:24,043
Something like Halli Galli?

1175
01:04:24,360 --> 01:04:26,505
- Sure.
- There's even a lie detector.

1176
01:04:27,397 --> 01:04:29,223
- That's...
- Is it dangerous?

1177
01:04:29,248 --> 01:04:32,225
- We need soju for that.
- We have soju.

1178
01:04:32,475 --> 01:04:34,601
- Soju?
- It's better than beer.

1179
01:04:34,626 --> 01:04:36,262
- Soju?
- Sure.

1180
01:04:37,338 --> 01:04:39,071
- Shall we begin?
- Yeah.

1181
01:04:39,893 --> 01:04:40,893
It'll be fun.

1182
01:04:41,585 --> 01:04:43,387
- Anyone tried this before?
- Not me.

1183
01:04:43,412 --> 01:04:46,114
Let's try it without the lie
detector first. We'll try to be honest.

1184
01:04:46,139 --> 01:04:47,410
- Sure.
- Okay.

1185
01:04:47,783 --> 01:04:49,117
I want to ask Da-Na.

1186
01:04:49,708 --> 01:04:53,210
Right now, is there someone
here in Love mansion who

1187
01:04:53,235 --> 01:04:58,961
is making it obvious that
he's interested in you?

1188
01:04:59,971 --> 01:05:01,440
I'm so curious, too.

1189
01:05:01,950 --> 01:05:03,815
(Curious)

1190
01:05:07,829 --> 01:05:08,829
No.

1191
01:05:09,666 --> 01:05:11,729
- Then you can say that.
- There isn't anyone.

1192
01:05:13,844 --> 01:05:15,574
- There isn't anyone.
- Really?

1193
01:05:18,397 --> 01:05:19,397
Ji-min.

1194
01:05:22,019 --> 01:05:25,099
You know the person you like?

1195
01:05:25,718 --> 01:05:26,718
Yeah.

1196
01:05:28,464 --> 01:05:31,397
Have you ever expressed
your liking for her?

1197
01:05:34,048 --> 01:05:37,428
Like, did you make it really obvious?

1198
01:05:38,219 --> 01:05:39,607
- No.
- No?

1199
01:05:41,188 --> 01:05:42,895
- You didn't express it at all?
- Yeah.

1200
01:05:42,920 --> 01:05:44,454
That means she doesn't know.

1201
01:05:44,479 --> 01:05:47,305
She asked if I made it
obvious. I never did that.

1202
01:05:48,118 --> 01:05:51,468
I was just curious about
her and tried to approach

1203
01:05:51,493 --> 01:05:54,645
her to the point where
she wasn't uncomfortable.

1204
01:05:55,245 --> 01:05:58,808
But I never expressed my feelings for her.

1205
01:06:01,331 --> 01:06:02,679
It's my turn? Gosh.

1206
01:06:05,429 --> 01:06:06,930
A hard question.

1207
01:06:07,422 --> 01:06:08,835
(Stare)

1208
01:06:09,641 --> 01:06:13,466
Did your feelings change a
lot while doing the challenges?

1209
01:06:13,491 --> 01:06:16,391
Wow, great question, Ji-min!

1210
01:06:16,416 --> 01:06:17,980
- Nice one.
- Who are you asking?

1211
01:06:18,005 --> 01:06:20,808
(Yang Ji-min is asking Ahn Ji-min.)

1212
01:06:22,795 --> 01:06:24,493
(Stare)

1213
01:06:24,708 --> 01:06:25,855
(Flustered)

1214
01:06:25,880 --> 01:06:28,180
- If he says yes, he's making it obvious.
- Be honest.

1215
01:06:28,205 --> 01:06:30,048
Wow, that's a really good question.

1216
01:06:33,992 --> 01:06:35,261
No.

1217
01:06:35,993 --> 01:06:38,152
- Seriously?
- Yeah. My feelings didn't change.

1218
01:06:38,592 --> 01:06:39,965
- For real?
- yeah.

1219
01:06:43,401 --> 01:06:46,598
(The girl who Ji-min is
interested in is still a mystery.)

1220
01:06:46,623 --> 01:06:47,974
I have no idea.

1221
01:06:51,829 --> 01:06:52,829
Let me ask you.

1222
01:06:53,282 --> 01:06:55,776
The second person who gave
you a good first impression?

1223
01:06:55,801 --> 01:06:57,127
"I'm kind of attracted to him."

1224
01:06:57,612 --> 01:06:59,239
Not the first person. The second one.

1225
01:06:59,750 --> 01:07:02,147
Does that mean she has to say his name?

1226
01:07:03,158 --> 01:07:04,880
(Anticipation)

1227
01:07:05,529 --> 01:07:09,976
The second guy is...

1228
01:07:10,001 --> 01:07:12,515
Ji-min.

1229
01:07:13,809 --> 01:07:14,915
(Shocking answer)

1230
01:07:14,940 --> 01:07:16,003
She's honest!

1231
01:07:16,028 --> 01:07:19,095
But isn't he the first
guy and not the second?

1232
01:07:19,452 --> 01:07:20,683
Ji-min.

1233
01:07:22,019 --> 01:07:23,344
That also makes me feel strange.

1234
01:07:25,467 --> 01:07:29,524
- His heart flutters.
- He's not 100 percent happy.

1235
01:07:29,787 --> 01:07:31,807
- Who's before me?
- But he doesn't hate it either.

1236
01:07:31,832 --> 01:07:34,267
Just think of the fact that
there are three guys behind you.

1237
01:07:34,292 --> 01:07:36,786
I'm more concerned
because she said I'm No. 2!

1238
01:07:38,567 --> 01:07:39,813
He's hilarious!

1239
01:07:42,962 --> 01:07:47,695
I told him he was No. 2 in order to
let him know I'm interested in him.

1240
01:07:48,157 --> 01:07:50,482
- So that's it.
- Ah, that's why she did it.

1241
01:07:51,265 --> 01:07:52,614
Ugh, but I messed up.

1242
01:07:53,482 --> 01:07:57,608
No, you did the right thing. You need
to throw a pebble to create a ripple.

1243
01:07:57,804 --> 01:08:02,211
And from now on, whenever he
sees her, he'll keep thinking about it.

1244
01:08:02,236 --> 01:08:03,236
"I'm No. 2?"

1245
01:08:04,396 --> 01:08:07,225
She'll always be within his vision.

1246
01:08:07,250 --> 01:08:09,629
Right. She did a wonderful job.

1247
01:08:10,362 --> 01:08:11,362
It's nice.

1248
01:08:13,033 --> 01:08:16,327
- Oh, they're making it there.
- They're making it right away.

1249
01:08:18,308 --> 01:08:19,855
Gosh, this is nice.

1250
01:08:20,670 --> 01:08:22,986
That looks so god. I really love meat.

1251
01:08:24,911 --> 01:08:27,895
- It looks great.
- I'm being treated like royalty.

1252
01:08:27,920 --> 01:08:30,278
Finally Su-won can eat with Ha-neul.

1253
01:08:34,056 --> 01:08:35,285
Oh my god! Oh my god!

1254
01:08:35,310 --> 01:08:39,455
That's top blade meat, and
we added salmon on top.

1255
01:08:39,656 --> 01:08:40,902
Thank you.

1256
01:08:46,816 --> 01:08:47,974
- Is it good?
- Yeah.

1257
01:08:48,721 --> 01:08:49,768
It tastes different.

1258
01:08:50,271 --> 01:08:51,889
- Meat is the best, huh?
- Yeah.

1259
01:08:52,433 --> 01:08:53,687
(Nom)

1260
01:08:55,385 --> 01:08:57,319
- How is it?
- It's so good.

1261
01:08:58,273 --> 01:09:01,987
You had dinner alone yesterday,
but today, you're having a feast.

1262
01:09:02,012 --> 01:09:03,012
Yeah.

1263
01:09:04,848 --> 01:09:06,138
Completely different dinners.

1264
01:09:06,757 --> 01:09:08,717
She really seems like his girlfriend.

1265
01:09:09,735 --> 01:09:10,966
Looks good.

1266
01:09:11,851 --> 01:09:14,898
The baguette I prepared yesterday...

1267
01:09:16,647 --> 01:09:18,099
was laid out on the table.

1268
01:09:18,124 --> 01:09:19,324
- Really?
- Yes.

1269
01:09:19,349 --> 01:09:22,469
Honestly, I couldn't look
because I was embarrassed.

1270
01:09:22,954 --> 01:09:25,862
(Even if he thinks about it now,
last night's dinner was a nightmare.)

1271
01:09:25,887 --> 01:09:27,832
I didn't have the
confidence to look at you.

1272
01:09:28,383 --> 01:09:29,383
It's yummy.

1273
01:09:30,303 --> 01:09:32,027
What if you hadn't won?

1274
01:09:32,052 --> 01:09:35,018
It's hard to get a
chance to talk like this,

1275
01:09:35,043 --> 01:09:37,876
but I would've still
gone to chat with you.

1276
01:09:38,330 --> 01:09:39,330
(Beam)

1277
01:09:40,019 --> 01:09:43,705
When you came in the kitchen this
morning, I bumped into you a few times.

1278
01:09:44,581 --> 01:09:46,755
But I didn't talk to you, right?

1279
01:09:47,997 --> 01:09:51,776
(This morning, Su-won
was especially quiet.)

1280
01:09:52,338 --> 01:09:55,273
(Is it because of the
aftermath of last night's dinner?)

1281
01:09:55,298 --> 01:09:58,879
- You didn't say anything, so...
- You didn't either.

1282
01:09:59,399 --> 01:10:00,970
- Oh, really?
- Yeah.

1283
01:10:01,616 --> 01:10:03,584
Okay, I'll talk to you first from now on.

1284
01:10:04,200 --> 01:10:05,690
(Su-won makes a
peace offering first.)

1285
01:10:05,715 --> 01:10:08,136
Are they already dating?

1286
01:10:08,557 --> 01:10:10,362
Maybe they are but just lying to the crew.

1287
01:10:12,597 --> 01:10:15,287
Win the challenge tomorrow.
Although I don't know what we're doing.

1288
01:10:16,425 --> 01:10:18,281
What if I don't choose you though?

1289
01:10:18,306 --> 01:10:20,096
Well, then, I should go to bed early.

1290
01:10:20,326 --> 01:10:24,297
You can pick someone else, but
on the last day, you'll eventually...

1291
01:10:24,863 --> 01:10:26,720
- Ugh!
- What?

1292
01:10:27,667 --> 01:10:30,041
You're annoying. Why are you so confident?

1293
01:10:31,187 --> 01:10:32,758
I'm not confident. I'm just...

1294
01:10:34,645 --> 01:10:36,859
You did come here to
meet different people.

1295
01:10:36,884 --> 01:10:39,136
Right, right. That's true.

1296
01:10:44,161 --> 01:10:46,146
You should date other girls, too.

1297
01:10:49,914 --> 01:10:50,914
Okay, I will.

1298
01:10:51,787 --> 01:10:54,066
If you tell me to, I will.
I should listen to you.

1299
01:10:56,484 --> 01:10:57,944
If you tell me not to, I won't.

1300
01:11:06,972 --> 01:11:09,717
You know the two guys you said
you were interested in the beginning?

1301
01:11:10,408 --> 01:11:12,269
Are you still interested in the same ones?

1302
01:11:17,253 --> 01:11:19,752
It hasn't changed?

1303
01:11:24,414 --> 01:11:27,673
(Ha-neul can't answer right away.)

1304
01:11:28,995 --> 01:11:30,637
I was just asking.

1305
01:11:34,372 --> 01:11:36,838
He's not getting the answer he wants.

1306
01:11:39,538 --> 01:11:43,450
- Very weighty.
- My curiosity just got bigger.

1307
01:11:43,475 --> 01:11:44,970
It's a strange atmosphere.

1308
01:11:47,672 --> 01:11:51,594
(A night of truths with drinks)

1309
01:11:52,074 --> 01:11:53,074
Goodness.

1310
01:11:53,433 --> 01:11:55,536
It was fun even though we
didn't go on a date, right?

1311
01:11:55,561 --> 01:11:56,792
- How was it?
- I had fun.

1312
01:11:56,817 --> 01:12:00,389
Me, too. I think it's better to hang
out in a group than go on dates.

1313
01:12:00,414 --> 01:12:01,464
Right?

1314
01:12:01,791 --> 01:12:03,609
We got to find out
how a lot of people feel.

1315
01:12:03,634 --> 01:12:04,753
Exactly.

1316
01:12:04,778 --> 01:12:07,493
- I just wish...
- We all felt the same way, huh?

1317
01:12:07,551 --> 01:12:09,734
- This was better.
- It was fun.

1318
01:12:09,759 --> 01:12:12,029
Hanging out with everyone is much more fun.

1319
01:12:12,604 --> 01:12:14,183
It was really fun today, right?

1320
01:12:15,012 --> 01:12:16,012
Yup.

1321
01:12:16,506 --> 01:12:20,865
Everyone answered
honestly. I didn't expect that.

1322
01:12:21,892 --> 01:12:23,995
I'm really confused
about how I feel right now.

1323
01:12:24,672 --> 01:12:26,139
I'm full of certainty.

1324
01:12:27,016 --> 01:12:29,738
Who on earth is she?
I'm so curious!

1325
01:12:31,353 --> 01:12:33,330
I wonder who Won-jae likes.

1326
01:12:33,906 --> 01:12:36,239
Wow, but their dates
are taking forever.

1327
01:12:37,120 --> 01:12:38,557
Gosh, I'm curious.

1328
01:12:39,688 --> 01:12:41,363
- I'm curious.
- I'm curious.

1329
01:12:41,388 --> 01:12:44,031
I think they'll fall asleep right
away 'cause they're exhausted.

1330
01:12:46,756 --> 01:12:49,879
(Just then, Yeo-bin returns
after ending her date.)

1331
01:12:50,850 --> 01:12:52,738
- Are you all drunk?
- No!

1332
01:12:52,763 --> 01:12:54,726
- What did you do?
- What did you do?

1333
01:12:54,751 --> 01:12:57,339
- It's so foggy.
- Foggy?

1334
01:12:57,364 --> 01:12:59,357
- Foggy?
- You went to see something pretty then.

1335
01:12:59,382 --> 01:13:01,351
We couldn't see a single thing.

1336
01:13:01,376 --> 01:13:02,592
It was a bit regrettable.

1337
01:13:02,617 --> 01:13:03,784
Is it 'cause of the rain?

1338
01:13:03,809 --> 01:13:06,071
- Anyway, Jung-woo is really fun.
- Yeah.

1339
01:13:06,096 --> 01:13:07,843
He was hilarious!

1340
01:13:08,648 --> 01:13:11,528
As you know, he's a
freelance travel writer.

1341
01:13:11,553 --> 01:13:15,294
Maybe that's why. He's a bit sentimental.

1342
01:13:15,319 --> 01:13:18,282
But that matched well with me.

1343
01:13:18,353 --> 01:13:19,641
That's why it was funny.

1344
01:13:20,279 --> 01:13:22,239
I'm glad I chose him.

1345
01:13:24,449 --> 01:13:25,806
Poor In-seong.

1346
01:13:27,568 --> 01:13:30,827
(Su-won finishes her date
with Su-won and comes back.)

1347
01:13:32,561 --> 01:13:34,212
Where did you go, Ha-neul?

1348
01:13:34,237 --> 01:13:35,237
I went to eat.

1349
01:13:35,262 --> 01:13:37,493
- Where?
- Seriously?

1350
01:13:37,518 --> 01:13:40,027
- I had beef.
- I bet it was delicious!

1351
01:13:40,221 --> 01:13:43,722
Earlier, I mentioned I wanted to
go for a drive because it was raining.

1352
01:13:43,747 --> 01:13:46,145
- Yeah! - And that I wanted
to have a deep conversation.

1353
01:13:46,170 --> 01:13:47,575
- And you did that?
- Yup.

1354
01:13:47,959 --> 01:13:50,133
- Wow.
- We ate and talked.

1355
01:13:50,578 --> 01:13:51,961
That's awesome!

1356
01:13:52,660 --> 01:13:54,645
(Men's lodging)

1357
01:13:57,677 --> 01:13:59,660
- You're back.
- You were awake?

1358
01:13:59,972 --> 01:14:01,805
Don't worry. We had
a better time than you.

1359
01:14:01,830 --> 01:14:03,132
Really? That's great.

1360
01:14:03,157 --> 01:14:04,753
Did you get to talk a lot?

1361
01:14:05,224 --> 01:14:06,541
Yeah, I guess.

1362
01:14:07,780 --> 01:14:08,847
You look bright.

1363
01:14:09,123 --> 01:14:10,733
I was tired, but...

1364
01:14:11,669 --> 01:14:13,411
You feel energized 'cause of Ha-neul?

1365
01:14:13,436 --> 01:14:14,436
No, it's not that.

1366
01:14:18,023 --> 01:14:19,801
Did you put the Love Coin in the locker?

1367
01:14:20,253 --> 01:14:21,522
No, not today.

1368
01:14:22,129 --> 01:14:23,129
You have to.

1369
01:14:24,609 --> 01:14:26,426
- I told her.
- What did you say?

1370
01:14:26,751 --> 01:14:29,811
I said it'd be funny if we didn't pick
each other when we went on a date.

1371
01:14:30,544 --> 01:14:32,035
To her? So what did she say?

1372
01:14:32,060 --> 01:14:34,958
She was just like, "Yeah, it'd be funny."

1373
01:14:35,930 --> 01:14:37,227
How did it feel?

1374
01:14:38,130 --> 01:14:40,193
He must be really curious.

1375
01:14:41,013 --> 01:14:42,013
Feel?

1376
01:14:43,670 --> 01:14:46,335
(Why is Ji-min so curious about
So-won and Ha-neul's date...?)

1377
01:14:46,360 --> 01:14:48,083
(Just then, Jung-woo returns.)

1378
01:14:48,108 --> 01:14:49,464
Jung-woo is back, too.

1379
01:14:54,059 --> 01:14:55,622
I wonder how he feels.

1380
01:14:56,713 --> 01:14:59,395
I just... What should I do now?

1381
01:15:00,295 --> 01:15:03,533
- I don't know. I'm going to
start fresh. - Start fresh?

1382
01:15:04,696 --> 01:15:05,696
I don't know.

1383
01:15:06,011 --> 01:15:07,995
Start fresh?

1384
01:15:08,233 --> 01:15:11,751
- What does that mean?
- Did he change his mind?

1385
01:15:12,875 --> 01:15:13,875
Probably.

1386
01:15:14,082 --> 01:15:16,742
I think he did experience some changes.

1387
01:15:18,121 --> 01:15:21,794
(Room of Expressing Interests)

1388
01:15:22,879 --> 01:15:24,412
What do I seriously do?

1389
01:15:27,786 --> 01:15:30,877
(Jung-woo will choose
who he's interested in.)

1390
01:15:33,992 --> 01:15:34,992
In-seong!

1391
01:15:38,156 --> 01:15:40,563
- If he opened it, shouldn't be
put a coin in there? - No.

1392
01:15:40,588 --> 01:15:43,835
- Oh, he has to take it out. - He needs
to take it out and put it elsewhere.

1393
01:15:45,679 --> 01:15:47,965
He's wondering if he
should take it out or not.

1394
01:15:53,681 --> 01:15:57,364
(He can't easily reach a decision...)

1395
01:15:57,389 --> 01:16:01,114
(In-seong had always picked him
ever since the first meeting.)

1396
01:16:01,933 --> 01:16:04,903
- This is not good.
- Oh dear.

1397
01:16:07,552 --> 01:16:09,266
I think he'll be really confused.

1398
01:16:09,444 --> 01:16:11,610
- They had good times.
- Will he take it out?

1399
01:16:11,635 --> 01:16:14,398
(Who put him in a dilemma...?)

1400
01:16:18,747 --> 01:16:20,381
- He took it out!
- In-seong.

1401
01:16:20,822 --> 01:16:21,822
In-seong...

1402
01:16:22,122 --> 01:16:23,543
Where will you take it?

1403
01:16:24,944 --> 01:16:28,610
- Is he going to shut the door?
- He didn't shut it yet.

1404
01:16:30,060 --> 01:16:32,790
Seeing how he didn't shut
it, he must still be thinking.

1405
01:16:33,159 --> 01:16:34,310
Will he put it back?

1406
01:16:34,335 --> 01:16:36,986
- He's in front of Da-na's locker.
- It's Da-na's locker!

1407
01:16:38,824 --> 01:16:40,729
Gosh, he's having a really hard time.

1408
01:16:40,754 --> 01:16:42,191
Yeo-min? Da-Na? In-seong?

1409
01:16:45,595 --> 01:16:46,997
(Is Da-Na his fresh start...?)

1410
01:16:47,283 --> 01:16:48,483
Why did he pause?

1411
01:16:48,898 --> 01:16:49,898
Oh my gosh.

1412
01:16:49,923 --> 01:16:52,574
You're not going to suddenly put
a 60-second ad in here, are you?

1413
01:16:55,890 --> 01:16:59,970
He knows how important this decision is.

1414
01:16:59,995 --> 01:17:04,529
Right. And he's a Money
Catcher who came to find true love.

1415
01:17:04,781 --> 01:17:07,295
(That's why it's so hard to decide.)

1416
01:17:11,771 --> 01:17:15,533
(He eventually chooses Da-Na.)

1417
01:17:17,308 --> 01:17:18,539
(My goodness.)

1418
01:17:18,564 --> 01:17:21,293
He gave the coin to Da-Na.

1419
01:17:22,235 --> 01:17:23,768
He chose the newlyweds.

1420
01:17:24,396 --> 01:17:26,118
This is so interesting!

1421
01:17:27,962 --> 01:17:30,019
This drama is so fun.

1422
01:17:31,347 --> 01:17:34,618
(A few hours later, Da-Na
came to deliver her Love Coin.)

1423
01:17:38,853 --> 01:17:41,960
(Who is the first person
to take her heart...?)

1424
01:17:42,646 --> 01:17:45,035
She talked with Jung-woo the most.

1425
01:17:47,423 --> 01:17:50,777
(She heads towards a
locker without hesitation.)

1426
01:17:52,466 --> 01:17:54,338
(It's a locker that already has a coin.)

1427
01:17:56,741 --> 01:18:00,164
(Da-Na chose Jung-woo.)

1428
01:18:01,946 --> 01:18:04,201
This is also an intriguing drama.

1429
01:18:04,856 --> 01:18:06,467
What about In-seong?

1430
01:18:07,642 --> 01:18:10,177
We did kind of predict there
would be something between them.

1431
01:18:10,958 --> 01:18:12,402
Da-Na is very popular.

1432
01:18:12,427 --> 01:18:14,118
Yes, she is.

1433
01:18:14,143 --> 01:18:16,571
- All the guys seem to like her.
- Right?

1434
01:18:16,596 --> 01:18:19,852
Won-jae likes her.
Jae-hyung said she's his target.

1435
01:18:21,039 --> 01:18:23,072
And Jung-woo already
expressed his liking for her.

1436
01:18:23,097 --> 01:18:24,964
Su-won is all about Ha-neul.

1437
01:18:25,243 --> 01:18:28,786
Su-won and Ha-neul have
some things to settle, too.

1438
01:18:28,811 --> 01:18:32,160
Despite the fact that
they went on a nice date...

1439
01:18:32,185 --> 01:18:35,035
- Something's unsettling.
- Yes. They talked a lot,

1440
01:18:35,068 --> 01:18:38,983
but they faced a difficult atmosphere
where they don't seem to be connecting.

1441
01:18:39,008 --> 01:18:42,583
Su-won expresses how he feels,

1442
01:18:42,608 --> 01:18:47,165
but Ha-neul's lips are sealed.

1443
01:18:51,723 --> 01:18:54,675
(The next day)

1444
01:18:54,700 --> 01:18:56,100
- Oh!
- What's that?

1445
01:18:56,594 --> 01:18:57,660
It's coming out.

1446
01:18:57,685 --> 01:19:00,126
(Please go check your locker.)

1447
01:19:00,151 --> 01:19:02,031
What?

1448
01:19:16,517 --> 01:19:18,590
(Lee Ha-neul)

1449
01:19:37,978 --> 01:19:39,390
Come with me.

1450
01:19:40,306 --> 01:19:43,306
- I didn't get any coins.
- Really?

1451
01:19:43,331 --> 01:19:44,331
Yeah.

1452
01:19:46,012 --> 01:19:49,289
If he was going to be like this, why
did he say that in front of everyone?

1453
01:19:50,167 --> 01:19:53,294
I don't know what's going through his mind.

1454
01:19:54,647 --> 01:19:56,924
I feel like he made a fool out of me.

1455
01:19:58,635 --> 01:20:02,407
Before going to put my Love Coin in
the locker, I really thought long and hard.

1456
01:20:02,886 --> 01:20:07,291
That's why I kind of
understand Su-won's decision.

1457
01:20:07,692 --> 01:20:09,080
He probably had...

1458
01:20:10,390 --> 01:20:11,726
the same thought as me...

1459
01:20:11,751 --> 01:20:12,751
I'm so silly.

1460
01:20:16,933 --> 01:20:19,036
When Su-won was so straightforward with me,

1461
01:20:19,892 --> 01:20:22,483
the first thing I thought about
was how he could abandon me.

1462
01:20:23,557 --> 01:20:24,557
So...

1463
01:20:30,352 --> 01:20:33,510
"What if I really like him, but
his feelings for me change"?"

1464
01:20:34,880 --> 01:20:36,951
"Or what if this is all a lie?"

1465
01:20:38,455 --> 01:20:43,314
